title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Cash 5' game
maintext:
OKLAHOMA CITY (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Oklahoma Lottery’s “Cash 5” game were:
02-04-12-19-22
(two, four, twelve, nineteen, twenty-two)
